up-retouch-cropped.jpg 1071w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/aa4a0/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 1428w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/0019a/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 2106w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 714px) 100vw, 714px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 714px) 100vw, 714px\" srcset=\"/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/ca55b/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 179w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/328f4/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 357w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/257f9/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 714w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/f866a/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 1071w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/aa4a0/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 1428w,\n/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/0019a/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg 2106w\" src=\"/static/5093871e5fb86d28506b66f40dea7be3/257f9/DSC_5486-Marconi-group-retouch-cropped.jpg\" alt=\"Benjamin Marconi Honored\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>Agency CEO Bob Wills presented a check for $10,000 to Dane Marconi in honor of his father, fallen SAPD Detective Benjamin Marconi at our annual “Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser” on February 11th. Dane’s fiancé Katlyn was present as well as SAPD&#8217;s Family Assistance Officer Sgt Andrea Hardeman. The money is being donated to the San Antonio Police Officers Association’s Ben Marconi Memorial Fund. The SAPOA represents, preserves and protects the benefits earned through dedicated service in the community of San Antonio.</p>\n","title":"SAPD Detective Benjamin Marconi Honored at Annual Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"SAPD Detective Benjamin Marconi Honored at Annual Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser","url":"/sapd-d